if we have not any tag,
but we want to create a milestone (a specific point) on our project
we use released option on GITHUB (it's not git feature)
it is high level feature build on top of tags.

tags ----> select release button
we create a release as "v1.4"
it will create a new tag on the "LAST COMMIT".

Note: we can see releases on the home page of repository!
      (if we have only tag
       it does not not exist on home page!)
